'''Mount Etna''', located in [[Wikipedia:Sicily|Sicily]], Italy, is the largest active volcano in Europe. Although no scenes were filmed there, it was digitally scouted to capture plate photography for backdrops in the [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]] vs. [[Anakin Skywalker]] fight on [[Mustafar]] in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Conveniently, Etna erupted while filming was in progress, so Lucas sent a team to film lava flows to be used as moving backgrounds.

